<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior craig and lotte's car night}
<A>__{lotte drives.}
<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior maxine's apartment a bit later}
<A>__{the doorbell rings. maxine, in a sheer black nightgown, answers it. john malkovich stands there.}
<C>__{maxine}
<D>__{thanks so much for coming over.}
<C>__{malkovich}
<D>__{oh, i'm really glad you called.}
<A>__{maxine gestures for him to enter. as malkovich passes by her, she checks the wall clock. the time is 3:50.}
<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior craig and maxine's office night}
<A>__{lotte sits on the floor in the dark. she leans, out of breath, against the wall next to the portal and checks her watch. the time is 4:10. she pulls open the door.}
